title.rendered: Alticor Inc Receives National Safety Award for Zero Lost Workday Case Incident Rate

content.rendered: Alticor Inc was awarded a national “Certificate of Commendation” for Zero Lost Workday Case Incident Rate for 2012 from The Associated General Contractors of America (AGC).  This prestigious award recognizes the Alticor Inc organization for their continued committment to a safe work environment.

excerpt.rendered: Alticor Inc receives The Associated General Contractors of America (AGC) National Award for Zero Lost Workday Case Incident Ratee for 2012.
